Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.28,0:00:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助的查克拉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.57,0:00:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变化了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是我的复制品吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:22.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 竟然能够进行部分变化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是个了不起的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.03,0:00:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咒印的控制很熟练嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.85,0:00:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:35.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是君麻吕之后最强的复制品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:41.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没打算跟你争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:45.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想要和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.67,0:00:46.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.76,0:00:49.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.51,0:00:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你从这里带出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.33,0:00:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.02,0:01:00.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有他在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:03.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有他在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:08.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就无法离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.09,0:01:28.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.37,0:02:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子 你想去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.69,0:02:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想死的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不要往前走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.57,0:02:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有鬼住在那里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:45.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.39,0:02:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙叫天枰的重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那边
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个村子现在已经渺无人烟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:03:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近他的人没有能活着回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是吓唬你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.73,0:03:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是赶快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.37,0:03:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟过来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.34,0:03:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只能跟到这里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.47,0:03:21.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不要进来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.51,0:03:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回自己家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.59,0:03:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:48.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里的人 全都杀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:27.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:35.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.68,0:04:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.95,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君麻吕…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:30.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没打算跟你争斗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想把你带出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无法离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.75,0:06:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉这种家伙 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想逃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分啊 就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道不是你自己迷路了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是顺着你指的方向走下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是我欺骗了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗你对我能有什么好处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和佐助两人独处了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:38.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁…谁想过这种事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:44.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 不说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个来找重吾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.84,0:07:54.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:56.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟重吾一起冲到外面去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:07:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是佐助的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不会被轻易干掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.34,0:08:06.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾变强了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是自己投奔大蛇丸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了纠正吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纠正
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以肯定的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于重吾而言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.54,0:08:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸的据点就如同纠正设施一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.42,0:08:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾想纠正什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.05,0:08:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单来说 就像中毒一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单凭自己无法做到…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抑制杀人的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:41.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.10,0:08:52.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:56.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经无法离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.38,0:09:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:18.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 真是惊人的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为会被干掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.38,0:09:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君麻吕 我来这里是为了找你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去投奔大蛇丸大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.45,0:09:39.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸大人那里 你我这样的人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.97,0:09:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很孤独吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.77,0:09:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投奔大蛇丸大人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不会孤独了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我异于常人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.84,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己都无法控制
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道何时就会杀了同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会被干掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那么弱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.05,0:10:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不怕我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.46,0:10:05.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不怕你 重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.73,0:10:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做你的牢笼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.74,0:10:24.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有我在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的灵魂就是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.20,0:10:34.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.56,0:10:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 从你身体里提取的酵素
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能放入我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.20,0:10:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我跟你一样 有了咒印的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.93,0:10:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:57.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咒印不是谁都能适应的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不适应的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.20,0:11:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那样 我就会死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 就别尝试了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是治疗的一个环节
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:11.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直被疾病缠身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.36,0:11:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的咒印或许能缓解病毒的侵蚀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你的力量能够救我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用这么担心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.63,0:11:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.07,0:11:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是挚友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.88,0:11:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的力量没有拒绝我的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君麻吕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你留下我离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.12,0:11:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.38,0:11:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使用的能力跟之前不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.31,0:11:57.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变硬了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:58.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 水月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.17,0:12:02.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 是水月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如此 这家伙不好对付哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.65,0:12:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里不是为了打架
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来跟他谈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.44,0:12:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可不是光靠动嘴就能摆平的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是用力量把他带走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个都住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.37,0:12:28.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 同归于尽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…想被我杀掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.14,0:12:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那股杀意可是真格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:03.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷毙了 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:25.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把门锁上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.02,0:13:30.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾 我来这里只是为了把你带走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太胆小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 并非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.04,0:13:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想到外面去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.44,0:13:47.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人格分裂得太严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:51.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说过了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾自己无法控制杀人的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他无法控制自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.13,0:14:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实他根本不想杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道自己什么时候又想去杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.96,0:14:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我了 快把门锁上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:12.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾果然很危险啊 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.06,0:14:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他面前 我都无法安心走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.63,0:14:19.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个据点也废了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这里你就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不错 我不想再杀人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.65,0:14:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.55,0:14:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来做你的牢笼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会阻止你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.08,0:14:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能抑制我的冲动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有君麻吕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然君麻吕不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就不能离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君麻吕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.32,0:15:07.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得是竹取一族的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸很中意重吾和君麻吕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.04,0:15:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为实验体 他们一直呆在这个据点里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且君麻吕很强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为珍贵实验体的重吾暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.51,0:15:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说只有他才能毫发无伤地阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那个男人 应该已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君麻吕已经为我而死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.59,0:15:38.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为你而死…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:47.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波佐助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.45,0:16:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要派你这种病人去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:03.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前从没发生过…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.67,0:16:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代替我成为大蛇丸大人容器的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的就是把他带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.54,0:16:16.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他值得你这么做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能成为容器的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.92,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了我就只有他了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就像我的转生一般
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便拼上性命 也要把他带回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.54,0:16:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得感谢你啊 重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.28,0:16:37.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的力量让我更强大了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 重吾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 君麻吕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:06.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所构想的小队成员就到齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.51,0:17:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面 我将我的目的告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:21.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的目的 是杀掉晓的宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波鼬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.29,0:17:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是他的哥哥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我需要你们的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 不是强迫的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:35.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香燐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你之前说过还有别的事 打算如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:45.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细想了下也不着急的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香燐 坦率一点不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:53.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实你打算一直跟佐助在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事怎么可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁造的谣啊 谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 说中了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难怪你口齿不清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.00,0:18:06.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前你就对佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水月 别再招惹香燐了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.53,0:18:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说过要彼此合作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.67,0:18:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.56,0:18:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:21.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香燐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:27.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直跟着佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到雾隐七刀之一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.19,0:18:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波鼬的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:37.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干柿鬼鲛的大刀鲛肌让我拿到为止
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是为了收集刀啊 真无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.02,0:18:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:46.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重吾 你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.84,0:18:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君麻吕说佐助犹如他的转生一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.67,0:18:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且拼命保护了你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:19:00.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是个怎样的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.27,0:19:16.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙为什么还不回村呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助那家伙一心想复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了杀掉哥哥宇智波鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他会去接近晓的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:27.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.24,0:19:28.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:29.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后 我们四人就一起行动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.10,0:19:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起 这支小队的名称就叫作“蛇”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也尽快开始行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓捕晓的任务还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 为了碰到佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:54.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最直接的办法就是去找晓的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛇的目的只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:59.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 我们的目标是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:20:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.78,0:21:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来说说我还是小鬼时发生的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时代是忍界大战末期
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争将各国拖入泥潭 迟迟无法终结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.57,0:21:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而木叶也出现了战斗力不足的局面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事就是在那时发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我成为上忍后的首个任务
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.24,0:22:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集卡卡西外传 战场上的男孩人生 前篇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:08.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛞蝓大人 能问你一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.33,0:22:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛞蝓大人是怎么过来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:14.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起这个的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.23,0:22:17.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 马上去小樱他们那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.64,0:22:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:20.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.73,0:22:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.55,0:22:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然如此 可我走路很慢的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.47,0:22:30.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这阳光实在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.61,0:22:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛞蝓大怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:36.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盐 拿盐来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:39.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.16,0:22:41.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么辛苦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟大家的辛苦比起来 不算什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.52,0:22:49.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的不知情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 你也来道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.50,0:22:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.52,0:22:55.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:23:00.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是纲手大人用时空间忍术送我过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:03.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱的修行还远远不够啊
